DESCRIPTION:2026-07-01 18:00:00\n\n(métro Berri)\n\nhttps://www.openstree
 tmap.org/node/12034322502\n\nWhen: July 1st 2026\, 18:00\nWhere: 1685 rue 
 Sanguinet\, Montréal\nPrice: Free for all trans people but if you bring a
  cis friend tell them it's 5$ and pocket the money (or give it to us as a 
